rows.label: qst202715_msg0002
rows.name:
This...[ML:Dash ] This wasn't
supposed to happen, mo!

rows.label: qst202715_msg0003
rows.name:
Doraram was supposed to save
Alst...[ML:Dash ] save Alst, mo!

rows.label: qst202715_msg0004
rows.name:
But the demon that was supposed
to appear didn't, and we were
attacked by a hungry monster...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202715_msg0006
rows.name:
We didn't come here to
listen to your regrets...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202715_msg0007
rows.name: You can do that on your own later.

rows.label: qst202715_msg0008
rows.name:
Was there a Nopon named
Mimumu here, mo?

rows.label: qst202715_msg0009
rows.name:
Mimumu...[ML:Dash ] She was a
devout believer, mo.

rows.label: qst202715_msg0010
rows.name:
"Was"...?[ML:Dash ] Don't tell me she was
eaten by that monster, mo?!

rows.label: qst202715_msg0012
rows.name: She was a devout believer, mo.

rows.label: qst202715_msg0013
rows.name:
That's why Doraram recommended
her, and she was transferred
to the main branch, mo.

rows.label: qst202715_msg0014
rows.name:
Mo mo mo?! Where is
the main branch, mo?

rows.label: qst202715_msg0016
rows.name:
They should be performing the grandest
Rite of Erasure in the Vault of Heroes in
the Spirit Crucible Elpys right now, mo.

rows.label: qst202715_msg0017
rows.name:
This is bad, mo! If we don't hurry,
it'll be just like here, mo!

rows.label: qst202715_msg0019
rows.name:
We have to crash that
ridiculous ritual and bring
that foolish girl home.
